# Landing Page Guide

## Overview
The landing page section is built using UmiJS and Ant Design components. It focuses on marketing and user engagement.

## Key Features
- Hero Section
- Feature Showcase
- Contact Form
- Testimonials

## Directory Structure
- `src/pages/landing/` - Landing pages
  - `index.tsx` - Home page
  - `about/` - About page
  - `contact/` - Contact page

## Components
- Use Ant Design components
- Custom components in `components/landing/`
- Layout components in `components/layout/LandingLayout/`

## Data Management
- Use React hooks for simple state
- API calls in `services/landing.ts`
- Use `useRequest` hook for data fetching

## Performance
- Optimize images and assets
- Use lazy loading for components
- Implement proper caching

## Best Practices
1. Focus on user experience
2. Optimize for performance
3. Make it mobile responsive
4. Use TypeScript for type safety
5. Keep components modular

